Meet Erin Ovaskainen and Lily Laporte, two inspiring 10-year old hockey players who have done amazing things for their communities. ⁣
⁣
Erin works with a non-profit organization called Calling All Angels, a 100% volunteer-run group that serves free meals, clothing and veterinary services every other week to the homeless of Montreal. ⁣
⁣
And Lily generously decided with her family to donate their Christmas gifts this year to less fortunate children in their community. ⁣
⁣
We teamed up with @caroouellette13, @Nursey16 and @MeloDaoust15 to thank Erin and Lily for going #ALLOUT this holiday season! Happy #CCMAssists everyone!
